  <brief_title>Role of Skin Tests for the Diagnosis of Immediate Hypersensitivity Reactions Due to Iodinated Contrast Media</brief_title>
  <official_title>Role of Skin Tests for the Diagnosis of Immediate Hypersensitivity Reactions Due to Iodinated Contrast Media</official_title>
